===''Pokémon the Series''===
{{main|Leon (anime)}}
Leon is a recurring character in {{aniseries|JN}}. He debuted in ''[[JN012|Flash of the Titans!]]'', where he earned himself the title of Monarch, the strongest [[Pokémon Trainer]] in the {{pkmn|world}}, by winning the finals of the [[World Coronation Series]]. This inspired {{Ash}} to participate in the World Coronation Series as well in the hopes of getting to battle Leon, making him Ash's main [[rival]] for the [[series]].
